Nigeria Union Clash Kills 3, Cement Trucks Burned, Vanguard Says

-- B y   E l i s h a   B a l a - G b o g b o
-- 
2011-08-18T08:04:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-18/nigeria-union-clash-kills-3-cement-trucks-burned-vanguard-says.html
A clash between rival Nigerian
unions in the central town of Gboko yesterday led to the deaths
of three people and the burning of 50 Benue Cement Co. trucks,
Lagos-based  Vanguard  newspaper reported, citing eyewitnesses.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Elisha Bala-Gbogbo in Abuja at 
 ebalagbogbo@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net . 